IN THE RIVER.

307
00:12:54,845 --> 00:12:57,778
Joe: HEY, MIMI, YOU'RE THE ONE
WHO WAS HUNGRY AND TIRED

308
00:12:57,811 --> 00:12:59,778
AND HAD TO SIT DOWN
EVERY FIVE MINUTES.

309
00:12:59,811 --> 00:13:01,278
FINALLY,
THEY'RE ALL TOGETHER.

310
00:13:01,311 --> 00:13:03,078
I MUST TELL MYOTISMON.

311
00:13:16,211 --> 00:13:18,611
[ ROARS ]

312
00:13:21,911 --> 00:13:25,578
[ ROARS ]

313
00:13:27,778 --> 00:13:31,478
SOUND ASLEEP.
ALL RIGHT! HA!

314
00:13:33,345 --> 00:13:35,811
MYOTISMON WILL BE SO PROUD
OF MY WORK,

315
00:13:35,845 --> 00:13:38,945
MAYBE I'LL
GET A PROMOTION.

316
00:13:38,978 --> 00:13:40,211
[ GASPS ]

317
00:13:40,245 --> 00:13:42,145
DEMI DART!

318
00:13:42,178 --> 00:13:44,145
SORA, WATCH OUT!

319
00:13:44,178 --> 00:13:47,078
BIYOMON!

320
00:13:47,111 --> 00:13:49,411
NO, BIYOMON,
PLEASE WAKE UP.

321
00:13:49,445 --> 00:13:50,578
BIYOMON!

322
00:13:50,611 --> 00:13:52,578
SORA, I WILL PROTECT YOU.

323
00:13:52,611 --> 00:13:53,745
OH, NO.

324
00:13:53,778 --> 00:13:54,911
SORA, WHAT'S WRONG?

325
00:13:54,945 --> 00:13:57,045
OH, DEMIDEVIMON!

326
00:13:57,078 --> 00:13:58,478
AAH!

327
00:14:02,478 --> 00:14:03,811
HUH?
OH!
OH!

328
00:14:03,845 --> 00:14:05,211
AAH!
AAH!
AAH!

329
00:14:13,011 --> 00:14:15,245
HEY, WHAT IS THAT?

330
00:14:15,278 --> 00:14:17,178
[ SNARLS ]

331
00:14:25,545 --> 00:14:27,511
HA HA HA HA HA.

332
00:14:27,545 --> 00:14:30,411
DIGIDESTINED,
YOUR JOURNEY ENDS HERE.

333
00:14:30,445 --> 00:14:31,745
THAT'S IT.

334
00:14:31,778 --> 00:14:34,045
THAT'S THE THING
DEMIDEVIMON WAS TALKING TO.

335
00:14:34,078 --> 00:14:36,845
HE'S NOT A THING.
HE'S LORD MYOTISMON.

336
00:14:36,878 --> 00:14:38,811
MYOTISMON?

337
00:14:38,845 --> 00:14:40,311
THAT'S LORD MYOTISMON.

338
00:14:40,345 --> 00:14:43,778
HA HA HA HA HA.

339
00:14:43,811 --> 00:14:48,211
THESE DIGIDESTINED ARE
MAKING ME FEEL A LITTLE BATTY.

340
00:14:48,245 --> 00:14:50,011
GRISLY WING!

341
00:14:54,311 --> 00:14:56,245
COME ON, GUYS. LET'S GO!

342
00:14:56,278 --> 00:14:58,378
PEPPER BREATH!

343
00:14:58,411 --> 00:15:03,245
BLUE BLASTER!

344
00:15:03,278 --> 00:15:06,611
MOTIMON DIGEVOLVE TO...

345
00:15:06,645 --> 00:15:08,145
TENTOMON.

346
00:15:08,178 --> 00:15:09,811
SUPER SHOCKER!

347
00:15:10,260 --> 00:15:12,099
BOOM BUBBLE, POP.

348
00:15:13,204 --> 00:15:15,937
Mimi: THEY'RE STILL
COMING AFTER US.

349
00:15:16,137 --> 00:15:17,737
AAH! AAH!

350
00:15:17,770 --> 00:15:19,004
MIMI!

351
00:15:19,037 --> 00:15:21,937
PALMON DIGEVOLVE TO...

352
00:15:21,970 --> 00:15:24,937
TOGEMON!

353
00:15:24,970 --> 00:15:27,637
LET ME TRY
TO GET MY POINT ACROSS.

354
00:15:27,670 --> 00:15:29,737
NEEDLE SPRAY!

355
00:15:32,270 --> 00:15:33,704
WAY TO GO.

356
00:15:33,737 --> 00:15:36,670
GOMAMON DIGEVOLVE TO...

357
00:15:36,704 --> 00:15:40,704
IKKAKUMON!

358
00:15:40,737 --> 00:15:43,770
HARPOON TORPEDO!

359
00:15:49,404 --> 00:15:50,804
WOW! WAY TO GO!

360
00:15:54,404 --> 00:15:56,804
YOU CAN'T DEFEAT ME
THAT EASILY.

361
00:15:56,837 --> 00:15:58,837
CRIMSON LIGHTNING!

362
00:15:58,870 --> 00:15:59,970
AAH!

363
00:16:00,004 --> 00:16:02,437
HA HA HA HA HA.

364
00:16:02,470 --> 00:16:03,704
[ ROARS ]

365
00:16:03,737 --> 00:16:05,037
HA HA HA.

366
00:16:05,070 --> 00:16:06,504
AAH!

367
00:16:06,537 --> 00:16:07,970
OHH!

368
00:16:08,004 --> 00:16:09,970
HA HA HA HA HA.

369
00:16:10,004 --> 00:16:12,937
Joe: TAI,
HE'S JUST TOO STRONG FOR US.

370
00:16:12,970 --> 00:16:15,437
NOW WHAT?

371
00:16:15,470 --> 00:16:18,904
I'VE GOT TO DO SOMETHING
TO HELP THEM.

372
00:16:18,937 --> 00:16:20,237
HUH?

373
00:16:20,270 --> 00:16:22,870
I'M THE ONLY ONE LEFT
TO FIGHT MYOTISMON.

374
00:16:22,904 --> 00:16:24,370
Sora: IT'S NO USE.

375
00:16:24,404 --> 00:16:26,804
YOU CAN'T DO ANYTHING
IN YOUR CONDITION.

376
00:16:26,837 --> 00:16:28,670
PLEASE UNDERSTAND, SORA.

377
00:16:28,704 --> 00:16:30,337
I HAVE TO GO.

378
00:16:30,370 --> 00:16:32,304
BIYOMON, YOU CAN'T.
YOU'LL GET HURT.

379
00:16:32,337 --> 00:16:34,770
I WON'T LET YOU.
MY DECISION IS FINAL.

380
00:16:34,804 --> 00:16:37,237
SORA, WHY CAN'T
YOU UNDERSTAND?

381
00:16:37,270 --> 00:16:39,204
HUH?

382
00:16:39,237 --> 00:16:42,670
WHY CAN'T
YOU UNDERSTAND?

383
00:16:42,704 --> 00:16:45,137
<i>I ALWAYS THOUGHT</i>
<i>MY MOM WAS THINKING</i>

384
00:16:45,170 --> 00:16:46,670
<i>ABOUT HER FLOWER SHOP,</i>

385
00:16:46,704 --> 00:16:49,170
<i>BUT SHE WAS REALLY WORRIED</i>
<i>ABOUT ME GETTING HURT.</i>

386
00:16:49,204 --> 00:16:53,670
BIYOMON DIGEVOLVE TO...

387
00:16:53,704 --> 00:16:57,670
BIRDRAMON!

388
00:16:57,704 --> 00:16:58,970
OH!

389
00:16:59,004 --> 00:17:00,937
