390
00:17:00,970 --> 00:17:05,437
METEOR WING!

391
00:17:05,470 --> 00:17:08,604
CRIMSON LIGHTNING!

392
00:17:08,637 --> 00:17:10,837
BIRDRAMON!

393
00:17:10,870 --> 00:17:12,804
[ WAILS ]

394
00:17:12,837 --> 00:17:15,237
BIRDRAMON, NO!
I LOVE YOU!

395
00:17:18,004 --> 00:17:19,970
♪ DIGIMON --
DIGITAL MONSTERS ♪

396
00:17:20,004 --> 00:17:21,804
♪ DIGIMON ARE THE CHAMPIONS ♪

397
00:17:21,837 --> 00:17:24,137
♪ DIGIMON --
DIGITAL MONSTERS ♪

398
00:17:24,170 --> 00:17:25,804
♪ DIGIMON ARE THE CHAMPIONS ♪

399
00:17:25,837 --> 00:17:30,204
BIRDRAMON DIGEVOLVE TO...

