00:17:30,237 --> 00:17:33,270
♪ DIGEVOLVE
INTO ULTIMATE ♪

401
00:17:33,304 --> 00:17:36,270
♪ DIGIMON --
DIGITAL MONSTERS ♪

402
00:17:36,304 --> 00:17:39,237
♪ DIGIMON ARE THE CHAMPIONS ♪

403
00:17:41,004 --> 00:17:43,970
GARUDAMON!

404
00:17:44,004 --> 00:17:47,337
♪ DIGIMON ARE THE CHAMPIONS ♪

405
00:17:47,370 --> 00:17:48,537
♪ DIGIMON ♪

406
00:17:50,337 --> 00:17:53,237
