THAT GLOW COMING FROM?

407
00:17:55,770 --> 00:17:59,204
SORA, I CAN FEEL YOUR LOVE.

408
00:17:59,237 --> 00:18:02,170
IT'S MAKING ME STRONG.

409
00:18:02,204 --> 00:18:05,070
MY CREST -- IT GLOWS.

410
00:18:05,104 --> 00:18:07,904
<i>GARUDAMON IS THE ULTIMATE FORM</i>
<i>OF BIRDRAMON.</i>

411
00:18:07,937 --> 00:18:10,404
<i>SHE COMMANDS THE SKY</i>
<i>AND PROTECTS THE EARTH.</i>

412
00:18:10,437 --> 00:18:14,604
