<i>CALLED WING BLADE.</i>

413
00:18:14,637 --> 00:18:17,737
AH, WHY IS IT NOW
THE CREST OF LOVE GLOWS

414
00:18:17,770 --> 00:18:20,570
JUST AS I WAS ABOUT
TO CLAIM VICTORY?

415
00:18:20,604 --> 00:18:23,370
I'LL PROTECT YOU, SORA.

416
00:18:23,404 --> 00:18:25,837
♪ HEY, DIGIMON,
HEY, DIGIMON ♪

417
00:18:25,870 --> 00:18:28,037
WING BLADE!

418
00:18:28,070 --> 00:18:31,804
♪ CHAMPIONS
OF THE DIGITAL WORLD ♪

419
00:18:31,837 --> 00:18:34,804
[ Growls ] GRISLY WING!

420
00:18:34,837 --> 00:18:38,270
I DID NOT ANTICIPATE
SUCH STRENGTH.

421
00:18:38,304 --> 00:18:40,737
COME ON, EVERYONE.
CLIMB ON.

422
00:18:40,770 --> 00:18:42,204
HUH?

423
00:18:42,237 --> 00:18:44,304
NEXT TIME,
YOU WON'T ESCAPE.

424
00:18:58,132 --> 00:19:00,481
Tai: ALL YOU HAD TO DO
WAS STOP WORRYING ABOUT IT,

425
00:19:00,481 --> 00:19:02,447
SORA, AND YOU GOT
YOUR CREST TO WORK.

426
00:19:02,481 --> 00:19:04,947
Sora: WHEN BIYOMON WAS
IN DANGER OF GETTING HURT,

427
00:19:04,981 --> 00:19:09,181
I REALIZED THAT I WAS ACTING
JUST LIKE MY MOM.

428
00:19:09,214 --> 00:19:10,847
KNOW WHAT I REALIZE?

429
00:19:10,881 --> 00:19:13,014
MY MOM
LOVED ME ALL ALONG.

430
00:19:13,047 --> 00:19:15,014
AND IT WAS YOUR LOVE

431
00:19:15,047 --> 00:19:17,047
THAT HELPED ME
DIGEVOLVE, SORA.

432
00:19:17,081 --> 00:19:19,514
I'M GLAD.

433
00:19:19,547 --> 00:19:22,481
YOU SEE? YOU ARE CAPABLE
OF LOVE AFTER ALL.

434
00:19:22,514 --> 00:19:24,981
I FELT SOMETHING. IT WAS
YOUR LOVE SHINING THROUGH.

435
00:19:25,014 --> 00:19:27,314
I FELT SOMETHING, TOO.
IT MADE ME UNCOMFORTABLE.

436
00:19:27,347 --> 00:19:29,647
LOVE SHOULDN'T MAKE YOU
FEEL LIKE THAT.

437
00:19:29,681 --> 00:19:31,114
Mimi: THAT'S RIGHT.

438
00:19:31,147 --> 00:19:33,447
I KNOW WHY YOU
FELT UNCOMFORTABLE, JOE.

439
00:19:33,481 --> 00:19:35,414
THESE WERE IN YOUR POCKET.

440
00:19:35,447 --> 00:19:37,414
OH, I GUESS IT WASN'T LOVE.

441
00:19:37,447 --> 00:19:39,381
[ LAUGHTER ]

442
00:19:39,414 --> 00:19:42,347
Matt: <i>SORA JOINED UP</i>
<i>WITH US AGAIN,</i>

443
00:19:42,381 --> 00:19:44,347
<i>AND WE WERE CLOSER THAN EVER.</i>

444
00:19:44,381 --> 00:19:47,447
<i>WE FINALLY THOUGHT THINGS</i>
WERE GOING OUR WAY, AND THEN...

445
00:19:47,481 --> 00:19:48,814
HUH?

446
00:19:48,847 --> 00:19:49,881
[ MYOTISMON LAUGHS ]

447
00:19:49,914 --> 00:19:51,847
I KNOW THAT LAUGH.

448
00:19:51,881 --> 00:19:54,781
Myotismon: YOU FOOLISH
DIGIDESTINED.

449
00:19:54,814 --> 00:19:58,648
THE SEVEN OF YOU
